-- India Orders Probe of Commonwealth Games Organizers, Economic Times Says
-- B y   N a t a l i e   O b i k o   P e a r s o n
-- 2010-10-16T05:29:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-16/india-orders-probe-of-commonwealth-games-organizers-economic-times-says.html
Indian Prime Minister Manmohan Singh
has ordered a probe into the organizing committee of the
Commonwealth Games, the Economic Times reported, citing a note
from his office. The sports secretary has asked officials on the
committee to hold their posts to ensure they are available for
questioning by authorities who will investigate allegations of
corruption, the report said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
